{"tid":1469680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逃犯條例】數名被捕示威者手腳骨折　送北區醫院拘留治理","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:50:27.000Z","uid":17281,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"60716b14fd26eaa3e7ed49faecd7bea6052c07c0","tid":1469680,"uid":17281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>網傳30名年青人被用私刑逼認罪 骨折送北區不准聯絡家人</strong><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳訊息指，30多名年約16至18歲被捕年青人，被警方押送到北區醫院求診，年青人全部骨折，數人大腿骨折，一名年青人脊椎受壓並有失禁情況，懷疑遭人濫用私刑，有指該批年青人全部認罪，而且不被准許打電話與家人聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>多名示威者被扣新屋嶺 今午逾10人送北區</strong><br />\n<br />\n有指警方周末拘捕多人，並將部分扣留在新屋嶺扣留中心。據悉，今日下午有10多名被捕人士被押送往北區醫院接受治理。<br />\n<strong>數名示威者手腳骨折</strong><br />\n<br />\n據了解，大部分送院的示威者頸痛，現時警方在北區醫院看管著數名手腳骨折的示威者，他們目前情況穩定，但受警方監控。消息指，目前病房內「警察多過病人」。網傳有被捕人士脊椎受壓，據悉病房內並末有相關個案。此外，示威者可以致電聯絡家人，亦有人協助示威者尋求律師協助。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員林卓廷在fb上表示，已聯絡醫管局，要求全力確保病人權益，並立即跟進及回應市民的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最少9人留醫骨科病房 48小時僅獲准見律師一次</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港01記者今晚前往北區醫院，多名警員出入病房，記者接觸到五名在骨科病房留醫的被捕人士，其中一人右邊頭部受傷，貼有紗布。目前四人已保釋，保釋條件不一，他們表示，病房內共有9名被捕人士，當中一人手骨骨折。他們全部在銅鑼灣被捕，其後被扣留在新屋嶺扣留中心。一名被捕人士指，被捕時曾被警員以警棍打，但扣留時則沒有，然而在新屋嶺期間不准許見律師，送至北區醫院才得見面一次，再要求見律師遭拒。<br />\n<br />\n討論咁多尋日機場既事 點解唔關心下我地既義士 煲大件事<br />\n起碼俾義士知道我地無放棄佢地<br />\n數人大腿骨折呀 佢地係狗屋發生咩事 係咪需要我地關心下呀<br />\n唔好令義士變Condom <br />\n諗下一步點做之餘 對義士保持關注係必須<br />\n<br />\nSorry 平時只回覆不開post 但見到而家連登個個Post都&quot;討論&quot;緊下一步 無人提義士忍唔住開Post<br />\nSorry 用左支那01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/363488/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E9%80%81%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86?fbclid=IwAR3OXI7n3WPEO4CLecXT2oV4V1t0RwjBBbZLC-TYTRKVGHM44a-1jFMnFHA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F363488%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E6%258A%2598-%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%258B%2598%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%2590%2586%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3OXI7n3WPEO4CLecXT2oV4V1t0RwjBBbZLC-TYTRKVGHM44a-1jFMnFHA&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=e4869dd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/363488/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-%E9%80%81%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86?fbclid=IwAR3OXI7n3WPEO4CLecXT2oV4V1t0RwjBBbZLC-TYTRKVGHM44a-1jFMnFHA</a>"},{"pid":"855d40181419b5dba6d2509e563d34b926534711","tid":1469680,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:42:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43671f4ba26ee0217e5ab519dc1b82fdc824582a","tid":1469680,"uid":17281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"酷刑呀"},{"pid":"f5e08af7ed3404a12b5b9e245055ead4b970c4ed","tid":1469680,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（尋失物) 今日13/8 喺機場唔見咗個背囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de09abbd6b43961ccd8c06cabceb3533147dbd35","tid":1469680,"uid":17281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"酷刑呀"},{"pid":"821e1dcbc8dd88691d74b75299f09d9c13e6b40d","tid":1469680,"uid":24007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811750274c06f346f71899cad222504c893ffe6b","tid":1469680,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:34.000Z","msg":"721 811 不割 檢討"},{"pid":"80f7f5574e2532fc000bb11885873605b4204fa7","tid":1469680,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32d255fc5de5b4e053976746e4db838b04a0da05","tid":1469680,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:47:54.000Z","msg":"要推出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce7301794b9bb2c61464de6305f223f3769cb11","tid":1469680,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"義士俾人打到斷手斷腳盲眼。<br />\n你班冚家剷就同前線打大陸狗嘅割席。唉。"},{"pid":"341cd8cbd06e26682a26d0f677f635a4424f5a63","tid":1469680,"uid":17281,"like":0,"dislike":0